{"about_the_game":"<strong>H.O.G.S</strong> is an immersive fps where you play as a pig cop in a dystopian England ruled by pigs. You are a one-hog army sent to crush the insurgent groups that have emerged within the district of <strong>Runt's Litter</strong>. Engage enemies in fast-paced combat where the difference between life and death is a well-placed bullet, an object to the head, or a boot to the face.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Spacer.png?t=1723061784\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Steampage_Gif_03_edited_optimized_03.gif?t=1723061784\" /> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Throw objects, kick down doors or smash windows and flank from behind. <strong>Use the environment to your advantage.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Clever enemies</strong> use tables as cover, throw objects and hunt the player. You better get smart or get killed.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Spacer.png?t=1723061784\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Steampage_Gif_01_Edited_Optimized_03.gif?t=1723061784\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore the dark reality of a Post-Singularist England ruled by pigs in a <strong>story told through environmental details and context clues</strong>.<br></li><li> <strong>Levels are non-linear</strong>, featuring multiple paths to choose from when engaging the enemy. Will you sneak in from behind enemy lines or go guns-a-blazing through the front door.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Spacer.png?t=1723061784\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Steampage_Gif_02_Edited_Optimized_03.gif?t=1723061784\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Endless replayability</strong>; score mode, speedrun challenges and three achievements per level let you enjoy H.O.G.S for as long as you wish.<br></li><li> <strong>Compete with other players</strong> to get the best score or time on global breadboards. Will you be the best in the world? </li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2899270?t=1723061784","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1723061784","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723061784","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723061784","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"H.O.G.S depicts scenes of police brutality and contains themes such as oppression and social unrest that some players may find uncomfortable. H.O.G.S prominently features violent acts in it's game play. Frequent use of blood and gore are present  but can be disabled in the game's settings. "},"detailed_description":"<strong>H.O.G.S</strong> is an immersive fps where you play as a pig cop in a dystopian England ruled by pigs. You are a one-hog army sent to crush the insurgent groups that have emerged within the district of <strong>Runt's Litter</strong>. Engage enemies in fast-paced combat where the difference between life and death is a well-placed bullet, an object to the head, or a boot to the face.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899270/extras/Spacer.png?t=1723061784\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam